    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Wheeleriola perplexa gen. et sp. nov., the first member of Catotrichinae (Diptera Cecidomyiidae) found in New Zealand" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4410200> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4410200>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Male morphology of Wheeleriola perplexa, holotype. 1: Wing, dorsal. 2: Second flagellomere, lateral (x = area with sensilla in other Catotrichinae). 3: Palpus, lateral. 4: Genitalia, ventral. 5: Gonostylus, ventral. 6: Tegmen and aedeagal apodeme, ventral. Scale for 1, 0.5 mm; for 2–6, 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4410200/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

